Rating: 3
Delicious after a few changes. Like previous reviewers, I used coconut milk instead of water, and less then the recipe called for because I wanted a thicker dipping sauce. I also used brown sugar instead of white. I simmered everything together in a small pot and then chilled it overnight. It was even better after sitting. My guests devoured it.

